-
-## Binance Accounts
-
-### main
-- API Key: your_mainnet_api_key
-- Secret: your_mainnet_secret
-- Testnet: false 
-
-### testnet-dev
-- API Key: your_testnet_api_key
-- Secret: your_testnet_secret
-- Testnet: true
-
-### TOOLS.md Structure
-
-```bash
-## Binance Accounts
-
-### main
-- API Key: abc123...xyz
-- Secret: secret123...key
-- Testnet: false
-- Description: Primary trading account
-
-### testnet-dev
